Main idea: side-scroller, slayer game

Requirements
- Multiple classes (selected randomly at first, then maybe a menu)
  - warrior, mage
- Moving enemies (dragon, _,)
  - short distance (zombie)
  - long distance (robot turrets - mortar)
- dropped items 
  - potions (couple types: health, speed, magic)
  - ? better weapons/armor (if we finish)
  - ? portals? (if we want to)
- combat
  - ? combos - press certain buttons in combination
  to deal more damage
- 2D
-  Josh to draw pixel art


